<h2 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:20px;color:#1a1a2e;">
  We Couldn't Reach Your Post — Please Check
</h2>

<p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:15px;color:#333333;line-height:1.6;">
  Hi {{hunterName}},
</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;color:#333333;line-height:1.6;">
  We tried to verify your post for <strong>"{{bountyTitle}}"</strong>
  and it didn't load. The bounty has a PostVisibility rule, so we
  re-check the post on a schedule to confirm it's still live.
</p>

<!-- Status Badge -->
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:8px 16px;border-radius:4px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#1a1a2e;background-color:#ffc107;">
      Action May Be Needed
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:16px;background-color:#f8f9fa;border-left:4px solid #ffc107;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;">
      <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;">
        What We Saw
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;">
        <strong>{{channel}}:</strong> {{url}}
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;">
        Error
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;">
        {{errorMessage}}
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;">
        What To Do
      </p>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#333333;line-height:1.5;">
        If your post is still live and public, no action needed — we'll
        re-check in about 6 hours and the alert will clear automatically.
        If the post has been taken down or made private, please contact
        the brand to discuss next steps before the second check, or your
        submission may be auto-refunded.
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

{{#if actionUrl}}
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 16px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color:#6c63ff;border-radius:6px;">
      <a href="{{actionUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
        View Submission
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
{{/if}}

<p style="margin:16px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#999999;">
  This is an early warning, not a final decision — your earnings are still
  on track if the post stays live.
</p>
